name: Frog jump Frog Switch
description: Two groups of frogs lost their way and they need to find their way home,but they have to do it according to special rules,a frog can jump over only one frog forward or on lotus leaf forward,it cannot jump back,and if any one of them gets stuck there,the game is over. Try to help the frog get their destination lotus leaf.The yellow frogs need to stay on yellow lotus leaf while green frogs on green lotus leaf.
